ve.net.dcs.AttachmentScanner IS A PLUGIN THAT IMPLEMENTS 
THE INTERFACE 'SANE' TO SCAN DIRECTLY FROM IDEMPPIERE

FOR MORE INFORMATION
http://www.sane-project.org/
http://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scanner_Access_Now_Easy

REQUIREMENTS: 
HAVE INSTALLED AND CONFIGURED 'SANE' ON THE SERVER

FEATURES: 
SUPPORT ONLY FOR IDEMPIERE WEBUI